- Confirm `Get-ChildItem "$env:LOCALAPPDATA\Programs\MnemosyneC\resources\vcredist\vc_redist.x64.exe"` exists (the bundled file)
- Confirm VC++ registry key shows installed after: `Get-ItemProperty "HKLM:\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\VisualStudio\14.0\VC\Runtimes\x64"`
- Launch app, send chat message, confirm AI responds via `branch=BUNDLED_SPAWN`
- Screenshot of working AI response in packaged window

